          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "This function can be used if an unexpected error is caught while running a",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "test and it should be treated as a test failure. If an error is thrown",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "from a test function, it is automatically recorded as an issue and this",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "function does not need to be used.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
